{{!--
{
  "layout": "webring",
  "title": "Skits That Never Happened | Vibes DIY",
  "description": "Seven comedy sketch ideas filtered through a quiz and flashcard prospectus. None were greenlit. All of them should be apps.",
  "ogUrl": "https://good.vibes.diy/skits-never-happened/",
  "source": "skits-never-happened",
  "skits": [
    {
      "num": "01",
      "title": "WHAT TYPE ARE YOU?",
      "premise": "Personality Quiz",
      "desc": "A Weekend Update segment where the cast takes an AI personality quiz live on air. Every archetype is aggressively mid.",
      "punchline": "You got: The Person Who Knows What a Podcast Is. Cut to sad trumpet.",
      "prompt": "A personality quiz app where every possible archetype is mediocre. Questions feel important but the result is always some variation of fine. Share your result card."
    },
    {
      "num": "02",
      "title": "EXAM DRILL",
      "premise": "Confidence-Rated Flashcards",
      "desc": "Celebrity Jeopardy parody. Contestants rate their confidence before answering. The entire episode resolves without anyone answering a single question.",
      "punchline": "I'm a NOT SURE on this one, Alex.",
      "prompt": "Flashcard study app with three-level confidence rating: Known, Not Sure, Still Learning. Cards marked Not Sure reappear more frequently. Tracks per-session confidence trends. Exam prep framing."
    },
    {
      "num": "03",
      "title": "VOCAB DECK BUILDER",
      "premise": "AI-Generated Study Deck",
      "desc": "A Spanish tutor app that keeps hallucinating words. In Spanish, confidence is confianza. Hubris is also confianza. Your startup is also confianza.",
      "punchline": "The word for everything is confianza.",
      "prompt": "Flashcard deck builder. User types a topic and gets an AI-generated deck of 10-20 cards with front and back. Study mode with flip animation, Known and Still Learning buttons, session progress bar."
    },
    {
      "num": "04",
      "title": "QUOTE FLIP",
      "premise": "Pop Culture Flashcards",
      "desc": "Two roommates argue about who said a famous quote. One keeps flipping an index card for the reveal.",
      "punchline": "Final card: nobody, actually. Made up. —AI.",
      "prompt": "Pop culture quote guessing app. Show a famous or commonly misattributed quote, guess who said it, then flip for the reveal. Pre-seeded with surprising and wrong answers. Party framing."
    },
    {
      "num": "05",
      "title": "KNOWLEDGE CHECK",
      "premise": "AI-Generated Quiz",
      "desc": "A tech CEO explains their product during a 10-question quiz. Every question is about a different product. He aces them all.",
      "punchline": "None of them were his.",
      "prompt": "Topic quiz app. User types any topic and gets a 10-question multiple choice quiz generated by AI. Four options per question. Score screen shows right or wrong per question and overall percentage with retry."
    },
    {
      "num": "06",
      "title": "TIMED EXAM PRACTICE",
      "premise": "30 Seconds Per Question",
      "desc": "A game show where contestants have 30 seconds per question. But the producer keeps reading the instructions aloud.",
      "punchline": "Show ends before any questions are asked.",
      "prompt": "Timed practice exam app. 20 AI-generated questions with a 30-second countdown per question. Questions grouped into sections. Section-by-section score breakdown. Configurable pass threshold default 70 percent. Shows pass or fail verdict."
    },
    {
      "num": "07",
      "title": "TOY TO KEY",
      "premise": "The Ladder Concept",
      "desc": "Infomercial parody. Start with our TOY tier — play around! Then MID tier — still fun! Then KEY tier—",
      "punchline": "You've signed a 5-year contract and you're crying in the parking lot.",
      "isProduct": true
    }
  ]
}
--}}

<style>
  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Courier+Prime:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=optional");

  :root {
    --bg: #111010;
    --cue: #ffe135;
    --white: #f4f0e8;
    --dim: rgba(244,240,232,0.5);
    --rule: rgba(244,240,232,0.1);
    --red: #e03030;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: "Courier Prime", "Courier New", monospace;
    line-height: 1.55;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

  .layout { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

  /* ── topbar ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .topbar {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .topbar .brand {
    font-family: "Bebas Neue", impact, sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--cue);
  }
  .topbar .meta {
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  /* ── hero ────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .hero .kicker {
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cue);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: "Bebas Neue", impact, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 16vw, 10rem);
    line-height: 0.87;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero h1 .accent { color: var(--cue); }
  .hero .lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    color: var(--dim);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .hero .lead em { font-style: italic; color: var(--white); }

  /* ── list ────────────────────────────────────── */
  .list-header {
    padding: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(244,240,232,0.3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .list-header::before { content: "// "; }

  .sketch {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr 130px;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .sketch { grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .sketch .build { display: none; }
  }

  .sketch .num {
    font-family: "Bebas Neue", impact, sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.8rem;
    line-height: 0.85;
    color: rgba(255,225,53,0.15);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    padding-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .sketch .title {
    font-family: "Bebas Neue", impact, sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
  }
  .sketch .premise {
    font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .sketch .desc {
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--dim);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .sketch .punchline {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .sketch .punchline::before {
    content: "— ";
    color: var(--cue);
  }

  .sketch .build {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .build-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--cue);
    color: #111;
    font-family: "Courier Prime", monospace;
    font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    transition: background 0.12s, color 0.12s;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .build-btn:hover { background: var(--white); }
  .build-btn.red { background: var(--red); color: var(--white); }
  .build-btn.red:hover { background: var(--white); color: #111; }

  /* ── closing ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .closing {
    padding: 3.5rem 0 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .closing p {
    font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--dim);
    max-width: 660px;
  }
  .closing p em { font-style: italic; color: var(--white); }
  .closing .cue { color: var(--cue); }

  /* ── footer ──────────────────────────────────── */
  footer {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(244,240,232,0.2);
  }
  footer a { color: inherit; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--cue); }
</style>

<div class="layout">
  <header class="topbar">
    <a class="brand" href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">VIBES.DIY</a>
    <span class="meta">seven pitches · all rejected</span>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="kicker">Filtered by the Quiz &amp; Flashcard Prospectus · Seven Pitches</div>
    <h1>
      SKITS<br>
      THAT<br>
      <span class="accent">NEVER HAPPENED</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="lead">
      An <em>ideas prospectus</em> got run through a comedy filter. These seven sketches emerged. None were greenlit. All of them should be apps.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="list-header">Seven pitches · all rejected · all buildable</div>

  {{#each skits}}
  <article class="sketch">
    <div class="num">{{num}}</div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2 class="title">{{title}}</h2>
      <div class="premise">{{premise}}</div>
      <p class="desc">{{desc}}</p>
      <p class="punchline">{{punchline}}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="build">
      {{#if isProduct}}
        <a class="build-btn red" href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">This IS the product →</a>
      {{else}}
        <a class="build-btn" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 prompt}}">Build It →</a>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </article>
  {{/each}}

  <div class="closing">
    <p>
      The prospectus said <em>quiz</em>. The prospectus said <em>flashcard</em>. The prospectus said <em>toy, mid, key</em>. It did not say <em>sad trumpet</em> or <em>confianza</em>. And yet here we are. <span class="cue">Build any of these in about three minutes at Vibes DIY.</span> Or don't. The prospectus has no enforcement mechanism.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top:1.25rem;">
      Each <em>Build It →</em> button above contains the prompt that made the idea. Hit it and you'll land in the builder with that prompt pre-loaded. Describe your version instead — your subject, your framing, your punchline — and it builds that&nbsp;one.
    </p>
  </div>

  {{> newsletter}}
<footer>
    <span>Vibes.diy · <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">homepage</a> · <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/discord">discord</a></span>
    <span>// seven pitches · all rejected</span>
  </footer>
</div>
